LABWC DOTFILES DEPLOYMENT GUIDE

✅ IMPLEMENTATION STATUS:
   - Project configuration: ./dotfiles/labwc/rc.xml
   - System configuration: ~/.config/labwc/rc.xml  
   - Sync tool: scripts/dotfiles-sync.sh
   - Two-way sync between project and system

✅ FIXES APPLIED:
   1. Context menu right-click:
      - Titlebar Top Right Bottom Left: right-click → client-menu
      - Title context: right-click → client-menu
      - Root context: right-click → root-menu

   2. Double-tap/double-click separation:
      - <default/> loads standard labwc mouse bindings
      - No custom overrides for tap/click behavior
      - Standard tap/click behavior preserved

   3. Tap configuration:
      - tapButtonMap: lrm (left/middle/right)
      - Correct finger-to-button mapping

USAGE:
   diff    : Show differences between project and system
   push    : Copy project config → system (~/.config/labwc)
   pull    : Copy system config → project

Commands:
   scripts/dotfiles-sync.sh diff    # Check differences
   scripts/dotfiles-sync.sh push    # Deploy fixes
   scripts/dotfiles-sync.sh pull    # Restore system
